      "roundness": null,
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Phase 5: START SIDECAR (after warmup — this is the KEY moment)\n\nmetrics_port = driver.get_metrics_port(config)\nstart_sidecar(run_id, engine, model, metrics_host=config.host, metrics_port, engine_host=config.host)\nDB: sidecar_pid, run_started_at (← use THIS for Grafana chart alignment, not started_at)",
      "baseline": 54,
