      "roundness": null,
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "FINALLY BLOCK — Always runs (exceptions, cancellation, success)\nOrder: shim → sidecar → engine\n\n1. if ollama_shim: ollama_shim.terminate()\n2. if sidecar: sidecar.terminate()\n3. if spawn_result.owned: driver.teardown(config, spawn_result)  ← DELETE /run/{id} to agent\n4. if attach mode (owned=False): leave engine running (no-op)",
      "baseline": 64,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "cleanup-box",
      "originalText": "FINALLY BLOCK — Always runs (exceptions, cancellation, success)\nOrder: shim → sidecar → engine\n\n1. if ollama_shim: ollama_shim.terminate()\n2. if sidecar: sidecar.terminate()\n3. if spawn_result.owned: driver.teardown(config, spawn_result)  ← DELETE /run/{id} to agent\n4. if attach mode (owned=False): leave engine running (no-op)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "cleanup-box",
      "originalText": "FINALLY BLOCK — Always runs (exceptions, cancellation, success)\nOrder: shim → sidecar → engine\n\n1. if ollama_shim: ollama_shim.terminate()\n2. if sidecar: sidecar.terminate()\n3. if spawn_result.owned: driver.teardown(config, spawn_result)  ← DELETE /run/{id} to agent\n4. if attach mode (owned=False): leave engine running (no-op)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "isDeleted": false
    },
