      "roundness": null,
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "pending → starting (phase 2) → warming_up (phase 4) → running (phase 6) → completed (success)\n                                                                      → failed (unhandled exception)\n                                                                      → cancelled (CancelledError, DELETE /api/runs/{id})\nOn exception: status=failed, error_message populated. CancelledError falls through finally → cleanup always runs.",
      "baseline": 44,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "status-box",
      "originalText": "pending → starting (phase 2) → warming_up (phase 4) → running (phase 6) → completed (success)\n                                                                      → failed (unhandled exception)\n                                                                      → cancelled (CancelledError, DELETE /api/runs/{id})\nOn exception: status=failed, error_message populated. CancelledError falls through finally → cleanup always runs.",
